TWComponent.script: tw.local.sqlString select distinct LMA."NAME" as ManagedAssetName, LMA.MIME_TYPE as MIMEType, LMA."LENGTH" as ManagedAssetSize, LS.NAME as SnapshotName, LP."NAME" as ApplicationName from LSW_MANAGED_ASSET LMA, LSW_PO_VERSIONS LPV, LSW_SNAPSHOT LS, LSW_PROJECT LP where LMA.VERSION_ID = LPV.PO_VERSION_ID and LPV.BRANCH_ID = LS.BRANCH_ID and LS.PROJECT_ID = LP.PROJECT_ID and LS."NAME" is not null and LMA."LENGTH" > ? and LMA.MIME_TYPE in <#=tw.local.statusIN#> and LP.SHORT_NAME in <#=tw.local.appIN#> order by LMA."LENGTH" DESC
